---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Services" description="Acumatica ERP implementation, rescue projects, integration, and ongoing support from a 26-year veteran.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-navy pt-32 pb-16 lg:pt-40 lg:pb-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <p class="text-teal font-semibold text-sm tracking-wide uppercase mb-4">Services</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-6">
          Everything Acumatica.<br />Nothing else.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          From first deployment to rescue missions to complex integrations —
          one consultant, one relationship, zero runaround.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Implementation -->
  <section id="implementation" class="py-20 lg:py-28 scroll-mt-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
        <div>
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-teal/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-navy mb-4">Implementation</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-6">
            New Acumatica deployments done right the first time. Every implementation
            is scoped, built, and delivered by Steve — not handed off to a team you've
            never met.
          </p>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            From requirements gathering through go-live and beyond, you get a single
            experienced point of contact who understands your industry and has done
            this dozens of times before.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-warm rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-10">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-navy mb-6">What's included</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              <span class="text-sm text-text-muted">Requirements analysis and solution design</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              <span class="text-sm text-text-muted">Data migration and system configuration</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              <span class="text-sm text-text-muted">Custom reports and dashboards</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              <span class="text-sm text-text-muted">User training and go-live support</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              <span class="text-sm text-text-muted">Post-launch stabilization and optimization</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr class="mx-auto max-w-7xl border-slate-100" />

  <!-- Rescue -->
  <section id="rescue" class="py-20 lg:py-28 scroll-mt-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
        <div>
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-teal/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M16.023 9.348h4.992v-.001M2.985 19.644v-4.992m0 0h4.992m-4.993 0l3.181 3.183a8.25 8.25 0 0013.803-3.7M4.031 9.865a8.25 8.25 0 0113.803-3.7l3.181 3.182m0-4.991v4.99" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-navy mb-4">Rescue Projects</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Your implementation went sideways. Your previous consultant disappeared.
            You're half-live with broken workflows and a team that's lost confidence
            in the system. Sound familiar?
          </p>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            We specialize in taking over failed or stalled Acumatica projects.
            We diagnose what went wrong, stabilize what's broken, and build a
            realistic plan to get you across the finish line.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-warm rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-10">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-navy mb-6">Common rescue scenarios</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              <span class="text-sm text-text-muted">Stalled implementations with no clear path forward</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              <span class="text-sm text-text-muted">Failed go-lives requiring rollback and restart</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              <span class="text-sm text-text-muted">Consultant turnover leaving gaps in knowledge</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              <span class="text-sm text-text-muted">Broken integrations and data integrity issues</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr class="mx-auto max-w-7xl border-slate-100" />

  <!-- Integration -->
  <section id="integration" class="py-20 lg:py-28 scroll-mt-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
        <div>
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-teal/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.19 8.688a4.5 4.5 0 011.242 7.244l-4.5 4.5a4.5 4.5 0 01-6.364-6.364l1.757-1.757m9.193-9.193a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0l-4.5 4.5a4.5 4.5 0 001.242 7.244" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-navy mb-4">Integration</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Acumatica doesn't live in a vacuum. Your CRM, ecommerce platform, WMS,
            payroll — they all need to talk to each other reliably.
          </p>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            As a certified Celigo partner and experienced REST API and OData developer,
            we build integrations that work — and keep working after the first week.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-warm rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-10">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-navy mb-6">Integration methods</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              <span class="text-sm text-text-muted">Celigo iPaaS for enterprise integration flows</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              <span class="text-sm text-text-muted">REST API custom development</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              <span class="text-sm text-text-muted">OData queries and reporting integrations</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              <span class="text-sm text-text-muted">CRM, ecommerce, WMS, and payroll connectors</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr class="mx-auto max-w-7xl border-slate-100" />

  <!-- Support -->
  <section id="support" class="py-20 lg:py-28 scroll-mt-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
        <div>
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-teal/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.594 3.94c.09-.542.56-.94 1.11-.94h2.593c.55 0 1.02.398 1.11.94l.213 1.281c.063.374.313.686.645.87.074.04.147.083.22.127.324.196.72.257 1.075.124l1.217-.456a1.125 1.125 0 011.37.49l1.296 2.247a1.125 1.125 0 01-.26 1.431l-1.003.827c-.293.24-.438.613-.431.992a6.759 6.759 0 010 .255c-.007.378.138.75.43.99l1.005.828c.424.35.534.954.26 1.43l-1.298 2.247a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.369.491l-1.217-.456c-.355-.133-.75-.072-1.076.124a6.57 6.57 0 01-.22.128c-.331.183-.581.495-.644.869l-.213 1.28c-.09.543-.56.941-1.11.941h-2.594c-.55 0-1.02-.398-1.11-.94l-.213-1.281c-.062-.374-.312-.686-.644-.87a6.52 6.52 0 01-.22-.127c-.325-.196-.72-.257-1.076-.124l-1.217.456a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.369-.49l-1.297-2.247a1.125 1.125 0 01.26-1.431l1.004-.827c.292-.24.437-.613.43-.992a6.932 6.932 0 010-.255c.007-.378-.138-.75-.43-.99l-1.004-.828a1.125 1.125 0 01-.26-1.43l1.297-2.247a1.125 1.125 0 011.37-.491l1.216.456c.356.133.751.072 1.076-.124.072-.044.146-.087.22-.128.332-.183.582-.495.644-.869l.214-1.281z" /><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-navy mb-4">Ongoing Support</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Go-live isn't the end — it's where the real work begins. Your team
            needs training, your workflows need tuning, and new requirements
            will always come up.
          </p>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            We stay on as a long-term partner. No ticket queues, no hold music —
            just direct access to someone who already knows your system inside and out.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-warm rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-10">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-navy mb-6">Ongoing support includes</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              <span class="text-sm text-text-muted">User training and onboarding for new staff</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              <span class="text-sm text-text-muted">Workflow customization and optimization</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              <span class="text-sm text-text-muted">Troubleshooting and issue resolution</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              <span class="text-sm text-text-muted">Version upgrades and new feature adoption</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-20 lg:py-28 bg-navy">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white mb-4">
        Let's figure out what you need.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-slate-300 text-lg max-w-xl mx-auto mb-10">
        No pitch deck. No discovery committee. Just a direct conversation
        with the person who'll do the work.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-base font-semibold rounded-lg bg-teal text-white hover:bg-teal-dark transition-colors duration-200"
      >
        Get in Touch
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
